## 9. Champs types courants

### Input text / email / tel / textarea

Standard `{...form.register("field")}`. Toujours `autoComplete="..."` approprié (`name`, `email`, `tel`, `postal-code`).

### Select natif

```tsx
<select {...form.register("subject")} className="...">
  <option value="">Choisir...</option>
  <option value="devis">Demande de devis</option>
  <option value="info">Renseignement</option>
</select>
```

Schéma Zod : `z.enum(["devis", "info"])`.

### Select shadcn / custom

Utiliser `Controller` de react-hook-form pour les composants contrôlés (radix, custom) :

```tsx
import { Controller } from "react-hook-form";

<Controller
  control={form.control}
  name="subject"
  render={({ field }) => (
    <Select value={field.value} onValueChange={field.onChange}>
      <SelectTrigger><SelectValue /></SelectTrigger>
      <SelectContent>
        <SelectItem value="devis">Devis</SelectItem>
        <SelectItem value="info">Info</SelectItem>
      </SelectContent>
    </Select>
  )}
/>
```

### Date picker (react-day-picker)

```tsx
<Controller
  control={form.control}
  name="date"
  render={({ field }) => (
    <DayPicker mode="single" selected={field.value} onSelect={field.onChange} />
  )}
/>
```

Schéma : `z.date()` ou `z.string().datetime()` selon sérialisation.

### Checkbox (consent)

```tsx
<input type="checkbox" {...form.register("consent")} />
```

Schéma : `z.literal(true, { errorMap: () => ({ message: "Acceptation requise" }) })`.

### Fichier + preview

```tsx
const [preview, setPreview] = useState<string | null>(null);

<input
  type="file"
  accept="image/*"
  onChange={(e) => {
    const file = e.target.files?.[0];
    if (file) {
      setPreview(URL.createObjectURL(file));
      form.setValue("file", file);
    }
  }}
/>
{preview && <img src={preview} alt="Aperçu" className="mt-2 h-32 rounded" />}
```

Pas de schéma Zod pour File -> validation manuelle côté serveur (type, taille).

